text: Jana Andresíková (2 April 1941 - 19 October 2020) was a Czech actress. Andresíková was born in Kroměříž, Czech Republic. She was known for her roles in The Young Man and Moby Dick (1979), Giorgino (1994) and Arabela (1979–1981). Andresíková died on 19 October 2020 from COVID-19 in Mělník, Czech Republic at the age of 79.Actress Jana Andresíková died of covid ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1941 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in the Czech Republic Category:Czech movie actors Category:Czech television actors Category:Czech stage actors
